{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ ("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"unregisterForPushNotifications:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"text":" (^","kind":"text"},{"text":")(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSError","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSError"},{"text":" * ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"error"},{"kind":"text","text":")) "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"completion"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"completion","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Block called when unregistration completes."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Receives nil on success or an NSError on failure."}]}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Removes the device from receiving push notifications:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"orderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Notifies Pushwoosh servers to stop sending notifications to this device"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Removes the device token from Pushwoosh"}]}]}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use this when the user logs out, deletes their account, or explicitly disables notifications."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"anchor":"Example","text":"Example","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Unregister during user logout:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["class AuthenticationManager {","","    func logout(completion: @escaping (Result<Void, Error>) -> Void) {","        \/\/ Show loading indicator","        LoadingIndicator.show()","","        \/\/ First, unregister from push to stop receiving notifications for this user","        Pushwoosh.configure.unregisterForPushNotifications { [weak self] error in","            if let error = error {","                Logger.warning(\"Push unregistration failed: \\(error.localizedDescription)\")","                \/\/ Continue with logout even if unregistration fails","            }","","            \/\/ Clear user session","            self?.clearUserSession()","","            \/\/ Clear user tags","            Pushwoosh.configure.setTags([","                \"logged_in\": false,","                \"user_id\": NSNull(),","                \"email\": NSNull()","            ])","","            \/\/ Stop server communication if required by privacy policy","            if UserDefaults.standard.bool(forKey: \"clearDataOnLogout\") {","                Pushwoosh.configure.stopServerCommunication()","            }","","            LoadingIndicator.hide()","            completion(.success(()))","        }","    }","","    private func clearUserSession() {","        KeychainManager.shared.clearCredentials()","        UserDefaults.standard.removePersistentDomain(forName: Bundle.main.bundleIdentifier!)","        CoreDataManager.shared.clearUserData()","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"metadata":{"fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"unregisterForPushNotifications:"}],"externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)unregisterForPushNotifications:","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"unregisterForPushNotifications:","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Type Method","title":"unregisterForPushNotifications:","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"method"},"abstract":[{"text":"Unregisters the device from push notifications.","type":"text"}],"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/unregisterForPushNotifications:"},"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/unregisterforpushnotifications:"]}],"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK."}],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","role":"collection","type":"topic","title":"PushwooshCore","kind":"symbol"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/unregisterForPushNotifications:":{"abstract":[{"text":"Unregisters the device from push notifications.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"unregisterForPushNotifications:","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/unregisterforpushnotifications:","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/unregisterForPushNotifications:","kind":"symbol","title":"unregisterForPushNotifications:","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"text":"unregisterForPushNotifications:","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","abstract":[],"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","title":"PWConfiguration","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"PWConfiguration"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"}}}